Fig. \ref{SchottkInGaN_rev_Fig4} displays the electric field variation in the active layer and Figs. \ref{SchottkInGaN_rev_Fig5} \& \ref{SchottkInGaN_rev_Fig6} show the I-V characteristics with respect to the Indium composition and metal work function respectively.

